==Book of Mormon Movie==
In ''[[The Book of Mormon Movie, Vol. 1: The Journey]]'', adapted from First and Second Nephi, Laman was portrayed by [[Kirby Heyborne]]. The portrayals were highly influenced by [[Arnold Friberg]] paintings of the characters.

